Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:33.76,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Sme...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.79,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem, aby si sa ospravedlňoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:38.20,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Budem sa cítiť mizerne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:42.54,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebudem ti už robiť problémy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:45.91,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretože, ťa milujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:48.47,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura, Nemu ochorela!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:52.32,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Do úst Nemu-chan spadol lístok zo sakury?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.43,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.23,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to kvôli mne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:59.22,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím, Nemu-chan! Prosím otvor svoje oči!
